The day-to-day

Own the agentic finance build roadmap: identify, prioritise, build, test, and iterate on AI agents that replace manual finance workflows, using frameworks such as LangChain, CrewAI, or AutoGen, from prompt design through to production deployment

Design and maintain automated data pipelines connecting SAP, Abacum, and Citi, and build AI-driven validation layers ...

